./1997/9712208:\title{ON GRAVITATION AND QUANTA\thanks{{This is a slightly extended version (with a footnote added on December 19, 1997) of an Abstract submitted in March 1997 to the Eight Marcel Grossmann Meeting, Jerusalem, June 22-27, 1997.}}
