./1998/9802002:\title{TOPOLOGY OF 3-DIMENSIONAL SEIBERG-WITTEN THEORY% \thanks{{Presented by B.~B.\ at the Workshop: ``Gauge Theories of Gravitation'', Jadwisin, Poland, 4--10 September 1997.} }
